1
00:00:00,530 --> 00:00:04,930
[Fated Hearts – A Bite of Susha]

2
00:00:05,070 --> 00:00:08,000
[On-set of "Fated Hearts"] [Arranging a meal for Yixiao]

3
00:00:05,330 --> 00:00:08,119
Tell the kitchen to prepare a few more dishes.

4
00:00:08,410 --> 00:00:09,460
Your Highness,

5
00:00:09,460 --> 00:00:10,530
you helped her already—

6
00:00:10,530 --> 00:00:12,860
and now you're treating her to dinner too?

7
00:00:14,140 --> 00:00:15,770
[Tight-lipped—Say it!]

8
00:00:14,430 --> 00:00:15,830
What...

9
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:16,930
Cut.

10
00:00:16,670 --> 00:00:17,530
[Hmph] [None of your business]

11
00:00:16,930 --> 00:00:18,160
Who said I'm treating her to dinner?

12
00:00:18,040 --> 00:00:18,840
[Even he's not convinced himself]

13
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:19,960
Your Highness,

14
00:00:19,340 --> 00:00:20,840
[One more time]

15
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:20,960
you helped her already—

16
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:23,290
and now you're treating her to dinner too?

17
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:25,390
What do you mean, "treating her"?

18
00:00:25,390 --> 00:00:26,880
Don't I need to eat too?

19
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:28,100
Don't you need to eat?

20
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:30,250
Your Highness, I've already eaten.

21
00:00:30,250 --> 00:00:31,430
[Conversation going nowhere fast]

22
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,970
[Subordinate's wooden expression says it all]

23
00:00:36,570 --> 00:00:38,000
[Expressing deliciousness with pure facial acting]

24
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,930
[Satisfied]

25
00:00:40,700 --> 00:00:41,500
Come on, try it.

26
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:42,680
It won't taste good once it's cold.

27
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:43,810
[Picks up food]

28
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:45,930
Seems like

29
00:00:45,930 --> 00:00:48,460
you've taken care of quite a few girls before.

30
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:51,340
You've taken care of plenty of girls.

31
00:00:53,930 --> 00:00:54,950
[A new plate of meat] [Voice full of grievance]

32
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:56,520
You didn't let me have any just now.

33
00:00:55,010 --> 00:00:56,050
[Still sounding wronged]

34
00:00:56,550 --> 00:00:58,180
Bet the pan-fried ones taste even better.

35
00:00:58,180 --> 00:01:00,380
[A boy who can't resist good food]
